name: Ripple CEO Showcases XRP’s $1B ETF Success With Institutional Support
description: The brass-grafted Twins enact the Billion-Synch, kinetic symmetry around the spinning torus. As the regulated current validates the circuit, the structure blooms with volumetric golden dust—a cipher for institutional reality.
